Pulse â€“ Module Extraction AI Agent

An AI-powered documentation analysis tool that automatically extracts product modules and submodules from help/documentation websites and returns them in a structured JSON format.

This project is built as part of the Pulse â€“ Module Extraction AI Agent assignment.

ğŸ“Œ Problem Statement

Modern software products have extensive help documentation spread across multiple pages.
The goal of this project is to:

Crawl documentation websites

Identify key product modules

Group related submodules

Generate accurate descriptions

Return the result in a clean, structured JSON format

All extraction is done only from the provided documentation URLs, without hallucination.

